<div class="welcome-page" onload="checkRegistration()">
    <header class="header">
        <%- include("partials/nav") %> 
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="left-side">
                <h1 class="heading-primary">
                    <span class="heading-primary__main">Natural</span>
                    <span class="heading-primary__main">Disaster</span>
                    <span class="heading-primary__main">Pet</span>
                    <span class="heading-primary__main">Care</span>
                </h1>
                <div class="cta">
                    <p class="heading-secondary">Find help from locals today</p>
                    <a href="/#about" class="cta__search-btn">Learn more!</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right-side">
                <div class="login-container">
                    <div class="login-container__icon-container">
                        <svg class="login-container__icon">
                            <use xlink:href="../pictures/sprite.svg#icon-user"></use>
                       </svg>
                       <p class="login-container__text">Sign In</p>
                    </div>
                    
                   <form action="/users/login" method="POST" class="login-form" autocomplete="off">
                        <input name="email" class="login-form__input" type="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                        <input name="password" class="login-form__input" type="password" placeholder="Password" required>
                        <input class="login-form__submit" type="submit" value="Login">
                    </form>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </header>


    <main class="main">
        
        <div class="about" id="about">
            <div class="about__left-side">
                <h2 class="about__heading heading2">Why we started PetSafe</h2>
                <h3 class="about__subheading subheading">A place to find help and give back to your community</h3>
                <p class="about__text1 paragraph">
                    Every year people are forced to abandon their homes and spend days or weeks in shelters 
                    due to fires, floods, tornadoes, and other natural disasters. In a best case scenario, 
                    you might have a friend or family member who can take in your pet. In the worst case, 
                    you are forced to leave them behind. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="about__right-side">
                <img src="/pictures/dog.jpg" alt="dog looking out window" class="about__dog-img" role="presentation">
                <img src="/pictures/cat.jpg" alt="cat on stairs" class="about__cat-img" role="presentation">
                <p class="about__text2 paragraph">
                    We want to provide people with the opportunity to find locals in their community who 
                    would be willing to foster their beloved pets so that they can spend more time staying 
                    safe and less time worrying about the furry members of their family.  The process is easy. 
                    Simply sign up for an account and you will be both a volunteer and eligible to receive help. 
                    We get what we give. In times of crisis, we must band together and help each other in whatever 
                    way we can.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact" id="contact">
            <h2 class="contact__title heading2">Let's connect!</h2>
            <form action="" class="contact__email-form">
                <input name="name" class="contact__input" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required>
                <input name="email" class="contact__input" type="email" placeholder="Your email" required>
                <textarea name="message" id="message" cols="30" rows="10" placeholder="Message" class="contact__message"></textarea>
                <input class="contact__submit" type="submit" value="Send Message">
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="faq" id="faq">
            <h2 class="faq__title section-title heading2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq__container">
                <div class="faq__accordian">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="question" id="question1" class="faq__input">
                        <label for="question1" class="faq__label">How do I volunteer to help?</label>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__add-outline" name="add-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__remove-outline" name="remove-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p class="faq__text">
                                Click on the Register Button on the navigation menu and sign up for an account. 
                                If anyone in your area needs help with their pets, they will be able to send you 
                                an email with a request.  It will be up to each person to decide if they wish to help.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="faq__accordian">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="question" id="question2" class="faq__input">
                        <label for="question2" class="faq__label">What if I need help but donâ€™t have the resources to help others?</label>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__add-outline" name="add-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__remove-outline" name="remove-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p class="faq__text">
                                While signing up for PetSafe does require you to be willing to receive emails from other users,
                                there are no requirements for responding to emails. You will remain anonymous to other users unless
                                you choose to respond to their emails.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="faq__accordian">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="question" id="question3" class="faq__input">
                        <label for="question3" class="faq__label">What if no one is in my area that can help me?</label>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__add-outline" name="add-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__remove-outline" name="remove-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p class="faq__text">
                                Unfortunately, we cannot guarantee help as this app relies on the participation of locals for its success. 
                                In the event that no one is available, please contact your local animal shelter to find information about pet
                                drop off locations near you.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="faq__accordian">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="question" id="question4" class="faq__input">
                        <label for="question4" class="faq__label">What kind of animals can be fostered during emergencies?</label>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__add-outline" name="add-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__remove-outline" name="remove-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p class="faq__text">
                                This site caters to people with the most common pets which are dogs and cats. Feel free to include other
                                animals in your request for help if necessary. It is possible that someone will be able to care for them
                                in an emergency situation.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="faq__accordian">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="question" id="question5" class="faq__input">
                        <label for="question5" class="faq__label">How do I know the person I am contacting is legitimate?</label>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__add-outline" name="add-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <ion-icon class="faq__remove-outline" name="remove-outline"></ion-icon>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p class="faq__text">
                                While we try to make sure that everyone who signs up is legitimate, you should be as careful as possible 
                                when meeting a stranger. Always meet in a public area and be sure to exchange relevant information before 
                                giving your pet to someone you do not know.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <%- include("partials/footer") %> 
    
    
</div>

